title: Chris Matthews: ‘Why Would Anybody Believe’ Trump After His Years of Birtherism?
text:
Chris Matthews: ‘Why Would Anybody Believe’ Trump After His Years of Birtherism? by Josh Feldman | 8:10 pm, February 27th, 2017 
During a discussion tonight on President Trump ‘s war with the press, Chris Matthews asked why anyone would believe Trump after his years of pushing birtherism. 
The Boston Globe ‘s Indira Lakshmanan said Trump’s attacks on the press using anonymous sources is somewhat ironic when he spoke of anonymous sources back when he was making Barack Obama ‘s birthplace an issue. 
Watch above, via MSNBC.
